                        </div>
                        <div class="instruction-item">
                            <strong>Waist:</strong> Measure around the narrowest part of the natural waistline.
                        </div>
                        <div class="instruction-item">
                            <strong>Hip:</strong> Measure along the fullest part of the hips.
                        </div>
                        <div class="instruction-item">
                            <strong>Shoulder:</strong> Measure across your shoulders, from right shoulder point to left shoulder point.
                        </div>
                        {% if chart_category == 'trouser-mens' %}
                        <div class="instruction-item" style="grid-column: span 2;">
