                    <p>All garments have little to no margin. If you are on the borderline between two sizes, we suggest you order a larger size for a relaxed fit. However, please remember the larger size can always be altered if needed.</p>
                    <p class="tolerance">Disclaimer: A tolerance of +/- 1 inch is acceptable for garment measurements when worn.</p>
